{"tha-ap12:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap12:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap12:0.3":"Anandattheraapadana ","tha-ap12:1.1":"“Aramadvara nikkhamma, ","tha-ap12:1.2":"padumuttaro mahamuni; ","tha-ap12:1.3":"Vassento amatam vutthim, ","tha-ap12:1.4":"nibbapesi mahajanam. ","tha-ap12:2.1":"Satasahassam te dhira, ","tha-ap12:2.2":"chalabhinna mahiddhika; ","tha-ap12:2.3":"Parivarenti sambuddham, ","tha-ap12:2.4":"chayava anapayini. ","tha-ap12:3.1":"Hatthikkhandhagato asim, ","tha-ap12:3.2":"setacchattam varuttamam; ","tha-ap12:3.3":"Sucarurupam disvana, ","tha-ap12:3.4":"vitti me udapajjatha. ","tha-ap12:4.1":"Oruyha hatthikhandhamha, ","tha-ap12:4.2":"upagacchim narasabham; ","tha-ap12:4.3":"Ratanamayachattam me, ","tha-ap12:4.4":"buddhasetthassa dharayim. ","tha-ap12:5.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap12:5.2":"padumuttaro mahaisi; ","tha-ap12:5.3":"Tam katham thapayitvana, ","tha-ap12:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap12:6.1":"‘Yo so chattamadharesi, ","tha-ap12:6.2":"sonnalankarabhusitam; ","tha-ap12:6.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap12:6.4":"sunotha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap12:7.1":"Ito gantva ayam poso, ","tha-ap12:7.2":"tusitam avasissati; ","tha-ap12:7.3":"Anubhossati sampattim, ","tha-ap12:7.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap12:8.1":"Catuttimsatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap12:8.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap12:8.3":"Baladhipo atthasatam, ","tha-ap12:8.4":"vasudham avasissati. ","tha-ap12:9.1":"Atthapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap12:9.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap12:9.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap12:9.4":"mahiya karayissati. ","tha-ap12:10.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap12:10.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap12:10.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap12:10.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap12:11.1":"Sakyanam kulaketussa, ","tha-ap12:11.2":"natibandhu bhavissati; ","tha-ap12:11.3":"Anando nama namena, ","tha-ap12:11.4":"upatthako mahesino. ","tha-ap12:12.1":"Atapi nipako capi, ","tha-ap12:12.2":"bahusacce sukovido; ","tha-ap12:12.3":"Nivatavutti atthaddho, ","tha-ap12:12.4":"sabbapathi bhavissati. ","tha-ap12:13.1":"Padhanapahitatto so, ","tha-ap12:13.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap12:13.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap12:13.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap12:14.1":"Santi arannaka naga, ","tha-ap12:14.2":"kunjara satthihayana; ","tha-ap12:14.3":"Tidhapabhinna matanga, ","tha-ap12:14.4":"isadanta urulhava. ","tha-ap12:15.1":"Anekasatasahassa, ","tha-ap12:15.2":"panditapi mahiddhika; ","tha-ap12:15.3":"Sabbe te buddhanagassa, ","tha-ap12:15.4":"na hontupanidhimhi te’. ","tha-ap12:16.1":"Adiyame namassami, ","tha-ap12:16.2":"majjhime atha pacchime; ","tha-ap12:16.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap12:16.4":"buddhasettham upatthahim. ","tha-ap12:17.1":"Atapi nipako capi, ","tha-ap12:17.2":"sampajano patissato; ","tha-ap12:17.3":"Sotapattiphalam patto, ","tha-ap12:17.4":"sekhabhumisu kovido. ","tha-ap12:18.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap12:18.2":"yam kammamabhiniharim; ","tha-ap12:18.3":"Taham bhumimanuppatto, ","tha-ap12:18.4":"thita saddhammamacala. ","tha-ap12:19.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap12:19.2":"buddhasetthassa santike; ","tha-ap12:19.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap12:19.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap12:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap12:20.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap12:20.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap12:20.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap12:21.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma anando thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap12:22.1":"Anandattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap12:23.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap12:24.1":"Buddho paccekabuddho ca, ","tha-ap12:24.2":"sariputto ca kolito; ","tha-ap12:24.3":"Kassapo anuruddho ca, ","tha-ap12:24.4":"punnatthero upali ca. ","tha-ap12:25.1":"Annasikondanno pindolo, ","tha-ap12:25.2":"revatanandapandito; ","tha-ap12:25.3":"Chasatani ca pannasa, ","tha-ap12:25.4":"gathayo sabbapindita. ","tha-ap12:26.1":"Apadane buddhavaggo pathamo. "}